SARS-CoV iyo MERS-CoV waxaa la ogaaday in ay kasoo jeedaan duqsiyada, waxaana loo gudbiyay dadka bisadaha iyo geela.
Marka la barbardhigo horumarinta SARS-CoV-2 ee fayraska kale ee corona, duqsiyada ayaa loo tixgeliyaa inay yihiin marti-geliyaha asalka ah ee SARS-CoV-2, iyadoo fayraska cusub uu 96% la mid yahay laba fayrus oo SARS-like ah oo ka yimaada duqsiyada oo loo yaqaan bat-SL-CoVZX45 iyo bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Si kastaba ha ahaatee, martida dhexdhexaadka ah ee ka caawisay fayraska inuu ka gudbo xadka noocyada kala duwan ee uu ku dhaco bini'aadamka weli lama oga, wali ma cadda wadada uu ku gudbi karo.
