Daawooyinkaas waxaa ka mid ah daawooyinka hadda jira iyo kuwa iman kara, daawooyinka ka hortaga fayraska, daawooyinka difaaca jirka, daawooyinka la isugu daro, plasma laga helo dadka ka soo kabsaday cudurka, daawooyinka Shiinaha, iyo taageero nafsaani ah.
