Xaqiiqdii, dadka ka bogsanaya cudurka waxay inta badan qabaan jirka ku jira antibody-yada ka hortaga cudurka.
Antibodies-ka waa immunoglobulins-ka (A.G.) ee ay sameeyaan unugyada biolymphocytic-ka si ay ula dagaallamaan sunta iyo jirrooyinka kale ee shisheeye, waxayna si toos ah u aqoonsadaan una difaacaan molecules-ka gaarka ah ee sunta.
