18-kii Febraayo, 2020, Booli Chang iyo la-hawlgalayaashiisa waxay daabaceen daraasad la barbardhigo daaweynta daawada reer galbeedka (WM) oo keliya iyo daaweynta wadajirka ah ee daawada reer galbeedka iyo daawada dhaqameed ee Shiinaha.
waxay ogaadeen in waqtiga ka soo kabashada heerkulka sare, xanuunka oo yaraada, iyo isbitaalka joogista ay aad uga gaaban yihiin kooxda daaweynta reer galbeedka iyo kuwa daweynta Shiinaha marka loo eego kooxda daaweynta reer galbeedka oo kaliya
Si aad u cajiib ah, heerka sii xumaanshaha calaamadaha (oo u dhaxeeya mid fudud iyo mid daran) ayaa aad uga hooseeyay kooxda daaweynta daawada reer galbeedka + daawada caadiga ah ee Shiinaha marka la barbar dhigo kooxda daaweynta daawada reer galbeedka oo keliya (7.4% marka la barbar dhigo 46.2%), heerka dhimashada ayaa aad uga hooseeyay kooxda daaweynta daawada reer galbeedka + daawada caadiga ah ee Shiinaha marka la barbar dhigo kooxda daaweynta daawada caadiga ah ee reer galbeedka oo keliya (8.8% marka la barbar dhigo 39%).
