Duqa magaalada Moscow, Mr. Sergey Sobyanin ayaa khamiistii ku dhawaaqay in magaalada la xirayo ilaa 1-da May.
Waddanka oo dhan, madaxweyne Vladimir Putin ayaa ku dhawaaqay in mushaharka dadka Ruushka ah ee aan shaqada imaan ay sii socon doonaan ilaa 30-ka Abriil.
Baarlamaanka Portugal ayaa u codeeyay in la kordhiyo xaaladda degdegga ah ee qaranka 15 maalmood; codbixinta waxaa lagu ansixiyay 215 cod, 10 cod ayaa laga reebay, hal cod ayaa laga diiday.
