Dukaamada Australia waxay hoos u dhigaan sicirka warqadda musqusha ee la iibsado
Dukaamada Australia ee Wal-worth iyo Coles ayaa habeenkii Sabtida iyo Axadda si weyn u adkeeyay xaddidaadda iibsiga waraaqaha musqusha si loo yareeyo laba duub dukaamada Wal-worth iyo hal duub dukaamada Coles ee macaamil kasta oo ka shaqeeya dhammaan laamaha dalka oo dhan.
Waxaan sidoo kale doortay hal dukaan oo Aldi ah, Isniinta.
Xayiraadahaas iibsiga waxaa lagu daabacay fariimo ay ku bixiyaan dukaamada iyo bogagga Facebook-ga.
Waxaa la sheegay in dadka iibsada ay u baaqday in la kaydiyo, cabsi laga qabo cudurka COVID-19 haddii ay dhacdo in dadka loo baahdo in ay is karantiimeeyaan.
Dukaamada Wall-Worths ayaa Arbacadii soo bandhigay xaddidaadyo ku saabsan warqadda musqusha ee guriga lagu geeyo si ay u noqoto hal duub halkii dalab.
Isbedeladaasi waxay ku yimaadeen xannibaadihii hore ee ay soo saartey dukaamada Wal-Worth ee 4-ta Maarso iyo dukaamada Kool's ee 5-ta Maarso, kuwaas oo u oggolaaday in la iibsado afar duub oo keliya.
Dukaamada Cools ayaa ku sheegay war-murtiyeedkooda 8-da Maarso in inkastoo ay ku xayiranyihiin afar duub, "dukaamo badan ayaa wali iibinaya wax walba oo ay haystaan hal saac gudahood markii la helo", waxayna ku tilmaameen dalabka "aan horay loo arag", sidoo kale dukaamada Aldi ayaa ku tilmaamay qoraal ay ku daabaceen Facebook-ka Talaadadii "aan la filayn".
Iibka ayaa "si weyn kor ugu kacay" usbuucii la soo dhaafay, sida uu sheegay afhayeenka dukaamada Wal-Worth.
Dukaanka Cosco ee magaalada Canberra ayaa toddobaadkii hore sheegay in la iibsan karo laba LFt.
Si loo yareeyo yaraanta, dukaamada Coles waxay dalbadeen alaab-qeybiyeyaal in ay keenaan duubyo waaweyn, waxayna kordhiyeen waqtiga gaarsiinta, dukaamada Wal-Worths waxay dalbadeen kayd dheeraad ah, halka dukaamada Aldi ay furteen kaydkooda si ay u helaan bandhigyo gaar ah oo lagu wado in la qabto Arbacada hore.
Russell Zimmerman, oo ah agaasimaha fulinta ee ururka ganacsatada Australia ayaa sheegay in ganacsatada ay isku dayayaan in ay kordhiyaan kaydka, laakiin xaddidaadaha ay ku xidhay golaha deegaanka ee la xiriira waqtiga gaarsiinta gawaarida ayaa adkeynaya.
Qiimaha wax soo saarka ayaa la filayaa inuu kor u kaco, iyadoo alaab-qeybiyeyaashu ay isku dayayaan inay buuxiyaan baahida, iyadoo ay yar yihiin waxyaabaha ay soo bandhigaan.
Talaadadii, dukaamada Aldi ayaa ku dhawaaqay in, sababtoo ah in alaabada la keeno goor hore, dukaamada qaar aysan awoodin inay bixiyaan dalab gaar ah Arbacada.
Dr. Gary Mortimer, oo ah khabiir ku takhasusay ganacsiga tafaariiqda ee jaamacada tiknoolajiyada Queensland, ayaa warbixin uu soo dhigay News.com.au, ku sheegay in dukaamada ay buux dhaafiyaan habeen kasta.
waxa uu tilmaamay in warqadda musqusha ay tahay badeecad aad u weyn taasoo keentay in kaydka uu hoos u dhaco marka loo eego tirada, markii la iibsado, waxa ay ka dhigeysaa meelo badan oo bannaan oo ku yaal khaanadaha, taasoo sii xoojinaysa dareenka yaraanta.
Russell Zimmerman, sida uu qoray ABC News, "Calls iyo Wallworths waxay leeyihiin aragti ah in haddii alaab badan ay ku jiraan khaanadaha, iyo haddii alaabada sida musqusha musqusha iyo jeermiska lagu iibsan karo oo lagu keydin karo, laga yaabo inay taasi yareyso argagaxa".
Shirkada Who Gives a Crap, oo soo saarta warqadaha musqusha ee dib loo isticmaalo, ayaa Arbacadii shalay sheegtay in kaydkoodu dhamaaday.
