Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa ku dhawaaqay in COVID-19 uu yahay cudur faafa.
Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa Arbacadii ku dhawaaqay in faafitaanka COVID-19, oo ah cudur ay keento fayraska coronavirus ee la xiriira cudurka neefsashada oo daran, oo loo yaqaan SARS-CoV-2, uu gaadhay heerka cudurrada faafa.
