Dabayaaqadii 1990-meeyadii iyo bilowgii qarnigii 21-aad, gacmo nadiifiyeyaasha aan biyo ku saleysanayn ee aalkolada leh ee lagu nadiifiyo gacmaha (oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha ee aalkolada leh, nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha nadiifiyeyaasha ama nadiifiyeyaasha gacmaha) ayaa bilaabay inay caan ku noqdaan.
Inta badan waxay ku saleysan yihiin isopropyl alcohol ama ethanol oo lagu daray maaddo qallajin ah sida karboomer (polymer acrylic acid) oo ku jira gel, ama qoyaan sida glycerin oo ku jira dareere, ama xumbo si loo fududeeyo isticmaalka loona yareeyo saameynta qallajinta khamriga.
