Marka hore, cilmi baadhayaashu waxay higsanayaan in ay sameeyaan tallaal dhamaystiran oo fayraska looga hortago.
Isticmaalka fayraska noocaas ah, ha ahaado mid aan firfircooneyn ama mid dhintay, waxaa loogu talagalay in lagu kiciyo jawaab difaac oo degdeg ah oo jidhka bini'aadamka ah ka dhanka ah cudurka cusub ee COVID-19.
Istaraatiijiyadda labaad, talaalka unugyada, waxa ay ku talo jirtay in la sameeyo tallaal uu difaaca jidhku dareemo unugyada qaar ee viruska.
Xaaladda SARS-CoV-2, cilmi baarisani waxay ku saabsantahay borotiinka SpikeS kaas oo ka caawiya viruska inuu galo Enzyme-ka ACE2.
Istaraatiijiyadda saddexaad waa tallaalka DNA (tallaalka RNA ama RNA, waa farsamo cusub oo lagu sameeyo tallaal).
Talaalada tijaabada ah ee laga helo mid ka mid ah xeeladahaas waa in la tijaabiyaa si loo hubiyo badbaadada iyo waxtarkooda. 16 Maarso 2020, tijaabadii ugu horreysay ee bukaan socodka ee tallaalka ayaa ka bilaabatay afar mutadawiciin ah Seattle.
